      <div class="hero-eyebrow">hello, world — I'm</div>
      <h1 class="hero-name">Joshua Jiménez</h1>
      <p class="hero-title" aria-hidden="true"><strong id="typewriter"></strong><span id="tw-cursor" style="color:var(--pink);font-weight:300;margin-left:1px;">|</span></p>
      <p class="hero-bio">
        I build things that actually work — clean APIs, reactive UIs, and pipelines built to scale.
        Currently building cybersecurity tooling at Pernix Solutions, finishing my B.Sc. in Computer Engineering at TEC.
      </p>
      <div style="display:inline-block;margin-bottom:22px;padding:5px 12px;background:rgba(124,255,107,.04);border:1px solid rgba(124,255,107,.14);border-radius:var(--radius-sm);font-size:.76rem;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;line-height:1.5;">
        <span style="color:var(--green-dim);">🥇 1st place</span><span style="color:var(--text-dim);"> · Gen AI &amp; Vibe Coding Hackathon · FAIR.CR · May 2026</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <span><span class="dot"></span> <span>Currently @ Pernix Solutions · Open to opportunities</span></span>
        <span>🎓 TEC — 2026</span>
        <span>📍 San José, CR</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">View My Work</a>
        <a href="/resume-joshua-jimenez.pdf" download class="btn btn-green">↓ Download CV</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get In Touch</a>
